              The

                Host Agent
                Host Agent Platform

              shall be able to generate an audit record of the following auditable events: 


Start-up and shut-down of the Host Agent;

Initial enrollment status with an Enterprise Management System (Success/Failure);

Change in enrollment state of a Host Agent;

other specifically defined auditable events

              .


The Host Agent shall operate with the following ESM Software;

  Endpoint Detection and Response


